                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header bg-secondary text-white">
                    <h3 class="h5 mb-0">Need More Help?</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Can't find what you're looking for? Try these resources:</p>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-github mr-2"></i> <a href="https://github.com/yourusername/securehealth/issues" target="_blank">GitHub Issues</a></li>
